{"tid":180462,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"女同學唔識充值張八達通","createTime":"2017-03-31T02:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T03:02:48.000Z","uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13ea401e85161eb04bad4b611a96840ede623097","tid":180462,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都係canteen 撞岩個女同學<br />\n咁就一齊排隊買早餐食<br />\n排到我地個時佢就話張八達通無錢<br />\n話可唔可以比住先<br />\n問佢有無現錢<br />\n佢就話比現錢會找返毫子<br />\n咁我見大家讀埋同一科幾好傾咪比住先<br />\n點知第二日食lunch佢又話負錢唔記得充值<br />\n唉咁無計<br />\n幫得一次好難話唔幫<br />\n然後今日佢又話八達通無錢<br />\n有無人知點先可以叫佢充值<br />\n我就黎破產"},{"pid":"6f8291bba756102269a64dd3511bbf1e23e4f58a","tid":180462,"uid":29037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"零分重作"},{"pid":"03792f45f97e57482426167aefa852646402b4f6","tid":180462,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"無是咁的"},{"pid":"eb95acee38ec479326f24aeb33b5a8cdabe0acf6","tid":180462,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051412293ae327ea5b484786002554be86041563","tid":180462,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"充你老母個值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0990af1ed233c7f7fcd476204c83c03d764e9b2f","tid":180462,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"充你老母值"},{"pid":"758bcf6111ef9f02c1262222589f4ff1c42ff756","tid":180462,"uid":38797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:02:31.000Z","msg":"叫佢用個西啫住先"},{"pid":"250b451ef3330b305752b9d731ad35e28d96dcec","tid":180462,"uid":38797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy